column2: SB Plays Six Ages 2: Lights Going Out - A Little Apocalypse, As A Treat
column7:
Surely we can distract ourselves from the grim truths of our every day lives by... living through ecological collapse at the end of a civilization....

Six Ages 2: Lights Going Out is a narrative strategy game in which you must help your clan survive as long as possible amidst the disasters and despair of a rapidly dying Glorantha. It's the end of the world, and all you can do is try to hang on as long as possible. Cheery!
Get it on Steam at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2278010/Six_Ages_2_Lights_Going_Out/

You can chat with other folks on the subreddit at https://www.reddit.com/r/SBMakesStuff
